## Development Workflow

### Git Workflow
- Feature branches: `feature/[ticket-id]-frontend`
- Bugfix branches: `fix/[ticket-id]-description`
- Commit messages follow Conventional Commits: `feat:`, `fix:`, `style:`, `test:`, `refactor:`

### Pre-commit Checklist
1. `npm run lint` — zero linting errors
2. `tsc --noEmit` — zero TypeScript errors
3. `npm test` — all unit/component tests pass
4. Update `ai-specs/specs/api-spec.yml` if new API calls were added

### Development Scripts
```bash
npm run dev           # Development server
npm test              # Unit and component tests
npm run test:e2e      # Cypress E2E tests
npm run cypress:open  # Cypress interactive mode
npm run build         # Production build
npm run lint          # ESLint
```
